				\begin{document}$$wPRS=\sum \limits_{i=1}^I{\beta}_i{G}_i$$\end{document}wPRS=∑i=1IβiGi, where βi is the per allele ORs derived from previous studies [16, 17, 33]. Additional information on the analysis of the interaction between the PRSGWAS and BMI trajectory is presented in the Additional file 1: Appendix S1.
